---
const sections = [
  {
    title: 'Servicios',
    links: [
      { name: 'TV por Internet' },
      { name: 'Cámaras de Seguridad' },
      { name: 'Diseño Web Pro' },
      { name: 'Energia Solar' },
    ],
  },
]
---

<footer class='bg-[#1E293B] text-gray-300'>
  <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto p-4'>
    <div class='xl:grid xl:grid-cols-3 xl:gap-8'>
      <div class='space-y-6'>
        <div class='flex items-center justify-center space-x-2'>
          <img class='w-10 h-10' src='/logo.webp' alt='Conectamos Logo' />
          <span class='text-xl font-bold text-secondary tracking-tight'
            >Conectamos</span
          >
        </div>
        <p class='text-sm max-w-xs'>
          Conectamos hogares y empresas con la fibra óptica más estable del
          mercado. Velocidad real, sin interrupciones.
        </p>
        <div class='flex space-x-5'>
          <a href='#' class='hover:text-secondary transition-colors'>Facebook</a
          >
          <a href='#' class='hover:text-secondary transition-colors'
            >Instagram</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='mt-12 flex gap-8 xl:mt-0'>
        <div class='md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-8'>
          {
            sections.slice(0, 2).map((section) => (
              <div>
                <h3 class='text-sm font-semibold text-primary tracking-wider uppercase'>
                  {section.title}
                </h3>
                <ul class='mt-4 space-y-3'>
                  {section.links.map((link) => (
                    <li>
                      <span class='text-base hover:text-white transition-colors'>
                        {link.name}
                      </span>
                    </li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='mt-12 flex gap-8 xl:mt-0'>
        <div class='md:grid md:grid-cols-1'>
          <div>
            <h3
              class='text-sm font-semibold text-primary tracking-wider uppercase'
            >
              Contáctanos
            </h3>
            <ul class='mt-4 space-y-3'>
              <li>
                <span
                  class='text-base flex flex-row gap-4 hover:text-white transition-colors'
                >
                  <svg
                    class='w-6 h-6'
                    fill='none'
                    viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                    stroke='currentColor'
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap='round'
                      stroke-linejoin='round'
                      stroke-width='2'
                      d='M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z'
                    ></path>
                  </svg> 315 65 74 722
                </span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span
                  class='text-base flex flex-row gap-4 hover:text-white transition-colors'
                >
                  <svg
                    class='w-6 h-6'
                    fill='none'
                    viewBox='0 0 24 24'
                    stroke='currentColor'
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap='round'
                      stroke-linejoin='round'
                      stroke-width='2'
                      d='M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z'
                    ></path>
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap='round'
                      stroke-linejoin='round'
                      stroke-width='2'
                      d='M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z'></path>
                  </svg> Cra. 3a #2-45
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class='mt-4 py-4 border-t border-gray-700 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center'
    >
      <p class='text-sm'>&copy; 2026 Conectamos.</p>
      <div class='md:mt-0 flex space-x-6'>
        <a href='#' class='text-xs hover:underline'>Términos y condiciones</a>
        <a href='#' class='text-xs hover:underline'>Política de privacidad</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
